cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with sentence generation and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it uses reinforcement learning and dynamic vocabulary prediction to improve efficiency. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it also deals with image captioning.
